295
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,920
misunderstand me even more?

296
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,000
When you're covered with lice,

297
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:15,960
you don't itch.

298
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:18,480
When you eloped with Qingqiu,

299
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,800
you two have already driven her crazy.

300
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,520
It's nothing to her this time.

301
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:23,520
Fine.

302
00:14:24,920 --> 00:14:27,200
[Invitation]
If Mrs. Lin tries to drive me away

303
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:28,840
with tons of gold

304
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:31,360
thrown in my face,

305
00:14:32,040 --> 00:14:34,240
I'd take Lin Qingqiu with me
and run again.

306
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:37,760
But my auntie has been
in charge of the mansion for years.

307
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,640
She's very careful with money.

308
00:14:40,040 --> 00:14:41,920
It would be more likely

309
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:42,920
that she throws wastewater at you.

310
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:47,240
I shall face it

311
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,520
whatever it will be.

312
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:51,200
Even if it's a trap,

313
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:52,600
it'd be a trap with delicious food.

314
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:53,880
Oh my...

315
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:01,840
Alas.

316
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:03,240
Qiu.

317
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:04,240
Father.

318
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,400
You've been kneeling for a whole night.

319
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,040
Wrapped your head around it yet?

320
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,280
I'm clearer than ever before.

321
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,720
I'll marry no one other than Lu Nanyi.

322
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,080
My son.

323
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:17,360
Don't challenge your mother on purpose.

324
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:19,080
It's my fault

325
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:20,560
to make her worry.

326
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:23,720
But Father,

327
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,440
life is long.

328
00:15:27,280 --> 00:15:29,240
If I can't grow old with the one I love,

329
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,360
I will die with regret.

330
00:15:34,160 --> 00:15:35,600
I totally understand

331
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:38,360
what is in your mind.

332
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,760
But does Miss Lu

333
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:41,240
share the same thoughts with you?

334
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,400
Have you ever thought about it?

335
00:15:45,640 --> 00:15:46,600
I'd say

336
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,240
you should apologize

337
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:49,440
to your mother.

338
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:50,800
Admit your mistake.

339
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,480
As for other matters,

340
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,640
let's discuss them later.

341
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:58,400
