342
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:00,240
This time,

343
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:02,840
I must show her my resolution.

344
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:04,640
Foolish.

345
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:07,560
Let me tell you the truth.

346
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:08,720
Your mother

347
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:10,320
has invited Miss Lu for a meeting.

348
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:11,520
No.

349
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:13,320
Nanyi must not see my mother.

350
00:16:13,560 --> 00:16:14,360
Halt it!

351
00:16:15,160 --> 00:16:16,000
