358
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:28,440
I galloped across battlefields,

359
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:29,360
slew countless enemies,

360
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,440
and achieved great military feats.

361
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:34,480
