the title of Prince of Anding.

362
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:36,440
But what good did it do?

363
00:16:36,920 --> 00:16:37,680
At home,

364
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:39,200
I still have to listen to your mother.

365
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:41,840
However,

366
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:43,440
after I leave,

367
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:46,400
whatever happens here

368
00:16:46,940 --> 00:16:48,200
cannot be blamed on me.

369
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,640
Thanks for your help, Father.

370
00:16:57,420 --> 00:17:00,620
[Elixir Tavern]

371
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:03,480
Mrs. Lin, you are the one
who maintains yourself well,

372
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,480
looking bright and beautiful.

373
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:08,120
I like your nice words the most.

374
00:17:12,520 --> 00:17:13,080
Madam,

375
00:17:13,080 --> 00:17:13,920
Miss Lu is here.

376
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,600
Here you are.

377
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:20,760
Greetings, Mrs. Lin.

378
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:21,960
Have a seat.

379
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:28,520
I heard that the desserts
are excellent here.

380
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:29,400
So today,

381
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,720
I specially invited Miss Lu

382
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:32,200
and Ruoxi to try them with me.

383
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:33,320
Here.

384
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:34,840
Try some peach blossom pastry.

385
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:35,920
Make yourself at home.

386
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:43,240
How do you like it?

387
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:44,640
Sweet and chewy.

388
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:45,520
Yummy.

389
00:17:46,040 --> 00:17:46,720
Oh.

390
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,560
Ruoxi.

391
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,000
Try some too.

392
00:17:56,120 --> 00:17:57,000
After you.

393
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:21,320
Ruoxi.

394
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:22,400
What do you think?

395
00:18:25,280 --> 00:18:26,480
The kind of pastry

396
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:28,960
should be made
with the freshest blossoms from March,

397
00:18:29,360 --> 00:18:30,440
ground into juice,

398
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:31,760
and then mixed with lard,

399
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:32,720
flour,

400
00:18:32,800 --> 00:18:33,840
and sweet bean paste to create.

401
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:37,080
But the pastry here

402
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:39,000
uses dried flowers past their season,

403
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:41,120
thus lacking a bit of freshness.

404
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:44,080
Mrs. Lin, if you like
peach blossom pastry,

405
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:46,480
I'll personally make some another day

406
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:47,480
and deliver them to your residence.

407
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:48,320
Great.

408
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:49,280
General Li's wife

409
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:50,720
and Minister Liu's wife

410
00:18:50,800 --> 00:18:51,440
told me

411
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:54,520
that Ruoxi makes
the best peach blossom pastry.

412
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,920
Then I'll expect to taste it.

413
00:18:57,760 --> 00:18:58,920
It's my honor

414
00:18:59,320 --> 00:19:00,600
to make you the pastry.

415
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:03,720
Oh.

416
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:04,520
Mrs. Lin,

417
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:05,680
