445
00:19:57,840 --> 00:19:58,700
That would suffice.

446
00:19:59,080 --> 00:20:00,040
Miss Lu.

447
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:02,880
You strike me

448
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:04,800
